message:
initial commit

MapReduce, Pig and Hive integration
add Cascading + MR section to README.md
update readme to reflect latest code changes

change ESStorage constructor to accept only Strings

fixes #34
add build status image (thanks to Karel)

address issue #3

add direct serialization of Jdk + Writable types
introduce serialization package similar to ES xcontent
add direct json serialization for pig types
add test for converting pig to json
rename PigValueWriter
add json serializer for Hive lazy types
add generic support for numbers
add timestamp as a future supported type
add support for Hive writable types
includes support for Hive 0.11 DecimalWritable
reuse key object inside RecordReader
integrate direct to json serialization into Hive and Cascading
introduce BytesArrays to easily pass/reference byte[]
improve Hive to JSON serialization bypassing byte[] copying
reduce the number of object copies created during serialization
improve logging for debug purposes
fix some tests along the way
remove old, to Object, serialization
update readme regarding the ES version required (0.90)
update readme regarding the YARN build
update bamboo image links (to avoid Github caching)
leave only one build status icon

Add integration with Apache Storm

Provide dedicated Bolt and Spout implementations
Related #267

Update README.md

Fixing typo in maven dependency
Closes #314
Signed-off-by: Costin Leau <costin.leau@gmail.com>

[DOC] Fix incorrect name

Fix incorrect statement in README.md
Fix #329

[DOC] Correct method name

MR Job class provides a `setOutputFormatClass` not `setOutputFormat` method
Fix #324

Changed elasticsearch.org URLs to equivalents at the new elastic.co site.

relates to #597

relates #609

Update README.md

Master requires JDK 8 for building (because of ES).
